NG0098:2: dam tshig mi bsrung tha mal sems //
NG0098:3: 'jig rten grags pa gtsor len pas //
NG0098:4: rang byung rig pa'i sems dang bral //
NG0098:5: mun gyur bden pa'i don las nyams //
NG0098:6: ji ltar btsal ba de nyid 'khrul //
NG0098:7: gang ltar bltas pa de nyid nor //
NG0098:8: lta log spyod rtsir mu stegs pa //
NG0098:9: shi nas dmyal ba chen por 'gro / thar pa'i skabs dang bral nas kyang *//
NG0098:10: theg chen gsang ba'i rigs dang bral //
NG0098:11: yang dag gsang ba'i don rtogs na //
NG0098:13: thams cad gsal ba'i me long pas //
NG0098:16: nam mkha'i mtha' dang mnyam pa'i rgyud chen po las //
NG0098:17: gdams ngag phog pa'i le'u ste nyi shu rtsa lnga pa'o ///
NG0098:18: / de nas yang sems dpa' rdo rje dam pas 'di skad ces gsol to //
NG0098:19: sangs rgyas kun gyi gsang ba'i gter //
NG0098:20: dus gsum rgyal ba'i dgongs pa'i lung *//
NG0098:21: gang zag dam pa gang ltar brtags //
NG0098:22: mgon po chen pos bshad du gsol //
NG0098:24: de nas de bzhin gshegs pa rdo rje sems dpas 'di skad ces gsungs so //
NG0098:26: rdo rje theg pa bshad dang nyan //
NG0098:27: skyon dang yon tan rim pa ni //
NG0098:28: rdo rje bla ma man ngag can //
NG0098:29: rig pa gsang ba'i mdzod 'dzin cing *//
NG0098:30: rang gsal lung gi don la goms //
NG0098:31: shes rig ye shes nyid du gsal //
NG0098:32: rna brgyud man ngag ldan pa dang *//
NG0098:33: rig pa mdzod kyi nyams dang ldan //
NG0098:35: rgyal thabs dbang thob man ngag ldan //
NG0098:36: spyod pa ma bcos klung du zhugs //
NG0098:37: thugs rjes 'gro ba sgrol la brtson //
NG0098:38: chos la phyogs ris mi mnga' zhing *//
NG0098:39: gsang ba'i man ngag 'tsho mkhas te //
NG0098:40: theg pa'i bye brag ma rmongs pas //
NG0098:41: lta ba'i che ba rtogs par ldan //
NG0098:42: tshig gcig don kun rtogs pa'i blo //
NG0098:44: bag chags phung po sreg byed pa //
NG0098:45: rdo rje bla mar yin par brtag / dregs dang snying rje chung ba dang *//
NG0098:46: rna brgyud gdams ngag mi ldan zhing *//
NG0098:47: thos chung khe grags bcud 'dzag cing *//
NG0098:48: dbang lung man ngag mi ldan pa //
NG0098:49: phongs pas phongs par gyur nas ni //
NG0098:50: man ngag dam pas phongs par 'gyur //
NG0098:51: dad pas lus srog mi blta zhing *//
NG0098:52: rdo rje bla ma gus pas khur //
NG0098:53: man ngag gsang ba gzhung ldan pas //
NG0098:54: gsang ba spel bar mi byed cing *//
NG0098:55: rang gsal rig pa'i don la dga' //
NG0098:56: bskal par mi 'gyur spun la sems //
NG0098:57: snying rje dam tshig ldan pa dang *//
NG0098:58: brtson 'grus shes rab ldan pa yis //
NG0098:59: rgyal tshab nges pa gcig la gtad //
NG0098:60: bla ma gzhung ldan mkhas pa yis //
NG0098:61: snod ldan rgyal sras de dag la //
NG0098:62: rang gsal ye shes don bshad na //
NG0098:63: skad cig nyid la rdzogs sangs rgyas //
NG0098:65: med chags pa che ba dang *//
NG0098:66: ser sna rang che phyogs blta zhing *//
NG0098:67: 'jig rten grags pa gnyer ba dang *//
NG0098:68: dam med brtson 'grus chung ba dang *//
NG0098:69: ye nas blo 'phang dma' ba dang *//
NG0098:70: 'jig rten bya ba'i rgyur sgrub dang *//
NG0098:71: theg pa dman par zhugs pa dang *//
NG0098:72: chos la phyogs ris ngoms skyen dang *//
NG0098:73: rdo rje bla ma bslu ba dang *//
NG0098:74: nges pa'i don la skur 'debs pa //
NG0098:75: 'di la gsang ba'i sgo phye nas //
NG0098:76: nor bu rin chen gang gtod pa //
NG0098:77: rdo rje dmyal bar skye bar nges //
NG0098:78: gal te thar zhing sems skyes na //
NG0098:79: gsang ba'i don dang phrad mi 'gyur //
NG0098:80: rdo rje bla ma smod pa ni //
NG0098:81: dus gsum rgyal ba smad pa'i mthus //
NG0098:82: bdun rgyud tshun chad brlag 'gyur nas //
NG0098:83: rdo rje 'bar ba'i nang du skye //
NG0098:0: [(]17[)]@#// btsal ba'i rnam grangs ci spyad kyang *//
NG0098:85: skyabs kyi dam pa rnyed mi 'gyur //
NG0098:86: gang zhig gsang ba'i gsung mchog la //
NG0098:87: gang zhig spangs shing skur btab pas //
NG0098:88: rgyal ba'i gsung mchog spangs pa yin //
NG0098:89: thar pa'i sems dang gtan du bral //
NG0098:91: nam mkha'i mtha' dang mnyam pa'i rgyud chen po las /
NG0098:92: gang zag brtag pa'i le'u ste nyi shu drug pa'o ///
NG0098:93: / de nas sems dpa' rdo rje dam pa des bcom ldan 'das la 'di skad ces gsol to //
NG0098:94: dus gsum rgyal ba'i sku gsung thugs //
NG0098:95: gsang mdzod thugs kyi me long 'di //
NG0098:96: bstan dang bshad dang bklag pa yi //
NG0098:97: yon tan rgya cher bshad du gsol //
NG0098:99: de nas de bzhin gshegs pa rdo rje sems dpas 'di skad ces gsungs so //
NG0098:101: dus gsum rgyal ba'i gter gyi dbyig / nam mkha'i mtha' dang mnyam pa'i rgyud //
NG0098:102: gsang ba'i yang snying bstan pa'i bcud //
NG0098:103: sangs rgyas kun gyi dgongs pa'i lung *//
NG0098:104: nges par gcig tu bstan pa'i rgyud //
NG0098:105: sku gsung nam mkha'i mtha' mnyam pa //
NG0098:106: spros bral bstan pa cir mi dgongs //
NG0098:107: theg pa'i yang rtse kun gyi 'grel //
NG0098:108: lung gsum man ngag kun gyi bcud //
NG0098:109: rin chen phung po zad mi shes //
NG0098:110: zag med ye shes bde chen klong *//
NG0098:111: rtag pa ye shes 'khor lo can //
NG0098:112: rab tu gsang ba rtogs dka' zhing *//
NG0098:113: dman pa'i spyod yul ma yin pa //
NG0098:114: rang gsal rang gi ye shes mdzod //
NG0098:115: rang byung rig pa'i 'od la zhugs //
NG0098:116: bde chen khyab pa'i ngo bo ni //
NG0098:117: nam mkhar 'dzin pa'i sems dang bral //
NG0098:118: 'di la mos pa'i gang zag ni //
NG0098:119: sangs rgyas sa la skal pa mnyam //
NG0098:120: rdo rje sems dpa' bcom ldan 'das //
NG0098:121: rang gsal khyab pa'i 'od mnga' zhing *//
NG0098:122: rig pa gsal ba'i dbyings la gnas //
NG0098:123: 'khor ba sangs rgyas dus gcig gsal //
NG0098:124: rig pa ye shes gsang bar snang *//
NG0098:125: 'gro drug ye shes snying por gsal //
NG0098:126: dngos po thams cad gsal bar rtogs //
NG0098:127: bstan pa'i snying po gang 'char ba //
NG0098:128: rgyal ba'i sku gsung thugs 'chang ba //
NG0098:131: ye shes nyi ma'i 'od ltar snyoms //
NG0098:132: thugs rjes 'gro ba'i dpal du shar //
NG0098:133: bdud dang bgegs kyis mi tshugs shing *//
NG0098:136: kun kyang bu bzhin skyong bar byed //
NG0098:137: de phyir bstan pa'i yang snying 'di //
NG0098:138: rigs nges rgyal tshab gcig la gtad //
NG0098:139: brag dang chu gting sba bya ste //
NG0098:140: srog dang bral ba'i kha bzhin bsdam //
NG0098:142: nam mkha'i mtha' dang mnyam pa'i rgyud chen po las /
NG0098:143: rgyud gzung ba'i le'u ste nyi shu rtsa bdun pa'o
NG0098:144: // // rgyud kyi rgyal po chen po rdo rje
NG0098:145: sems dpa' nam mkha'i mtha' dang mnyam par sbyor ba
